{
  "video_id": "Wgt8QUHQjw8",
  "title": "How your brain decides what is beautiful | Anjan Chatterjee",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13689.0,
      "end_time": 15656.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s 1878."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16789.0,
      "end_time": 20670.0,
      "text": "Sir Francis Galton gives a remarkable talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21138.0,
      "end_time": 25276.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s speaking to the anthropologic institute of Great Britain and Ireland."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25990.0,
      "end_time": 30160.0,
      "text": "Known for his pioneering work in human intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30400.0,
      "end_time": 32280.0,
      "text": "Galton is a brilliant polymath."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33536.0,
      "end_time": 35900.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s an explorer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35114.0,
      "end_time": 36867.0,
      "text": "an anthropologist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36891.0,
      "end_time": 38421.0,
      "text": "a sociologist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38445.0,
      "end_time": 40140.0,
      "text": "a psychologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40380.0,
      "end_time": 41511.0,
      "text": "and a statistician."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43207.0,
      "end_time": 45489.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s also a eugenist."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46420.0,
      "end_time": 47666.0,
      "text": "In this talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48627.0,
      "end_time": 53380.0,
      "text": "he presents a new technique by which he can combine photographs"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53404.0,
      "end_time": 55663.0,
      "text": "and produce composite portraits."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56483.0,
      "end_time": 61497.0,
      "text": "This technique could be used to characterize different types of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62522.0,
      "end_time": 67871.0,
      "text": "Galton thinks that if he combines photographs of violent criminals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67895.0,
      "end_time": 71210.0,
      "text": "he will discover the face of criminality."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72730.0,
      "end_time": 74590.0,
      "text": "But to his surprise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74840.0,
      "end_time": 76948.0,
      "text": "the composite portrait that he produces"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77771.0,
      "end_time": 79270.0,
      "text": "is beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81846.0,
      "end_time": 84874.0,
      "text": "Galton&#39;s surprising finding raises deep questions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85335.0,
      "end_time": 86919.0,
      "text": "What is beauty?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87890.0,
      "end_time": 94709.0,
      "text": "Why do certain configurations of line and color and form excite us so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96192.0,
      "end_time": 97720.0,
      "text": "For most of human history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97744.0,
      "end_time": 103299.0,
      "text": "these questions have been approached using logic and speculation."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103935.0,
      "end_time": 105452.0,
      "text": "But in the last few decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105476.0,
      "end_time": 108354.0,
      "text": "scientists have addressed the question of beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108378.0,
      "end_time": 113447.0,
      "text": "using ideas from evolutionary psychology and tools of neuroscience."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 114322.0,
      "end_time": 118185.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re beginning to glimpse the why and the how of beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 118765.0,
      "end_time": 122890.0,
      "text": "at least in terms of what it means for the human face and form."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123210.0,
      "end_time": 124577.0,
      "text": "And in the process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 124601.0,
      "end_time": 126953.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re stumbling upon some surprises."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 127980.0,
      "end_time": 130788.0,
      "text": "When it comes to seeing beauty in each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131569.0,
      "end_time": 135923.0,
      "text": "while this decision is certainly subjective for the individual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 135948.0,
      "end_time": 140131.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s sculpted by factors that contribute to the survival of the group."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 140630.0,
      "end_time": 143278.0,
      "text": "Many experiments have shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 143302.0,
      "end_time": 147303.0,
      "text": "that a few basic parameters contribute to what makes a face attractive."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148135.0,
      "end_time": 153810.0,
      "text": "These include averaging, symmetry and the effects of hormones."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 153835.0,
      "end_time": 156245.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take each one of these in turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 158351.0,
      "end_time": 159825.0,
      "text": "Galton&#39;s finding"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 159849.0,
      "end_time": 165131.0,
      "text": "that composite or average faces are typically more attractive"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 165156.0,
      "end_time": 168713.0,
      "text": "than each individual face that contributes to the average"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 168737.0,
      "end_time": 170666.0,
      "text": "has been replicated many times."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 171753.0,
      "end_time": 175941.0,
      "text": "This laboratory finding fits with many people&#39;s intuitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 176574.0,
      "end_time": 180785.0,
      "text": "Average faces represent the central tendencies of a group."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 181544.0,
      "end_time": 185863.0,
      "text": "People with mixed features represent different populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 185887.0,
      "end_time": 189235.0,
      "text": "and presumably harbor greater genetic diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 189259.0,
      "end_time": 191457.0,
      "text": "and adaptability to the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 192157.0,
      "end_time": 196561.0,
      "text": "Many people find mixed-race individuals attractive"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 196585.0,
      "end_time": 198759.0,
      "text": "and inbred families less so."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 200447.0,
      "end_time": 204630.0,
      "text": "The second factor that contributes to beauty is symmetry."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 205294.0,
      "end_time": 209620.0,
      "text": "People generally find symmetric faces more attractive than asymmetric ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 210578.0,
      "end_time": 215830.0,
      "text": "Developmental abnormalities are often associated with asymmetries."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 215854.0,
      "end_time": 219119.0,
      "text": "And in plants, animals and humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 219143.0,
      "end_time": 222449.0,
      "text": "asymmetries often arise from parasitic infections."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 223193.0,
      "end_time": 225411.0,
      "text": "Symmetry, it turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 225435.0,
      "end_time": 228938.0,
      "text": "is also an indicator of health."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 230289.0,
      "end_time": 231882.0,
      "text": "In the 1930s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 232599.0,
      "end_time": 235499.0,
      "text": "a man named Maksymilian Faktorowicz"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 235523.0,
      "end_time": 238700.0,
      "text": "recognized the importance of symmetry for beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 238724.0,
      "end_time": 240879.0,
      "text": "when he designed the beauty micrometer."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 242117.0,
      "end_time": 243268.0,
      "text": "With this device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 243292.0,
      "end_time": 246347.0,
      "text": "he could measure minor asymmetric flaws"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 246371.0,
      "end_time": 250920.0,
      "text": "which he could then make up for with products he sold from his company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 250944.0,
      "end_time": 254768.0,
      "text": "named brilliantly after himself, Max Factor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 254792.0,
      "end_time": 257803.0,
      "text": "which, as you know, is one of the world&#39;s most famous brands"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 257827.0,
      "end_time": 258995.0,
      "text": "for \"make up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 260334.0,
      "end_time": 264293.0,
      "text": "The third factor that contributes to facial attractiveness"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 264317.0,
      "end_time": 266300.0,
      "text": "is the effect of hormones."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 267353.0,
      "end_time": 271407.0,
      "text": "And here, I need to apologize for confining my comments"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 272102.0,
      "end_time": 273669.0,
      "text": "to heterosexual norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 275438.0,
      "end_time": 279908.0,
      "text": "But estrogen and testosterone play important roles"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 279932.0,
      "end_time": 282530.0,
      "text": "in shaping features that we find attractive."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 283463.0,
      "end_time": 287320.0,
      "text": "Estrogen produces features that signal fertility."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 288154.0,
      "end_time": 291104.0,
      "text": "Men typically find women attractive"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 291128.0,
      "end_time": 295429.0,
      "text": "who have elements of both youth and maturity."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 296300.0,
      "end_time": 299976.0,
      "text": "A face that&#39;s too baby-like might mean that the girl is not yet fertile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 300939.0,
      "end_time": 302912.0,
      "text": "so men find women attractive"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 302936.0,
      "end_time": 307171.0,
      "text": "who have large eyes, full lips and narrow chins"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 307196.0,
      "end_time": 308705.0,
      "text": "as indicators of youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 309520.0,
      "end_time": 312902.0,
      "text": "and high cheekbones as an indicator of maturity."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 314384.0,
      "end_time": 319667.0,
      "text": "Testosterone produces features that we regard as typically masculine."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 320597.0,
      "end_time": 322616.0,
      "text": "These include heavier brows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 322641.0,
      "end_time": 323946.0,
      "text": "thinner cheeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 323970.0,
      "end_time": 326222.0,
      "text": "and bigger, squared-off jaws."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 326246.0,
      "end_time": 328360.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s a fascinating irony."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 329515.0,
      "end_time": 330666.0,
      "text": "In many species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 330690.0,
      "end_time": 332700.0,
      "text": "if anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 332950.0,
      "end_time": 335787.0,
      "text": "testosterone suppresses the immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 336822.0,
      "end_time": 340996.0,
      "text": "So the idea that testosterone-infused features are a fitness indicator"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 341200.0,
      "end_time": 343245.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t really make a whole lot of sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 344300.0,
      "end_time": 346502.0,
      "text": "Here, the logic is turned on its head."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 347478.0,
      "end_time": 349627.0,
      "text": "Instead of a fitness indicator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 349651.0,
      "end_time": 353580.0,
      "text": "scientists invoke a handicap principle."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 354609.0,
      "end_time": 358140.0,
      "text": "The most commonly cited example of a handicap"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 358165.0,
      "end_time": 359656.0,
      "text": "is the peacock&#39;s tail."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 360362.0,
      "end_time": 364758.0,
      "text": "This beautiful but cumbersome tail doesn&#39;t exactly help the peacock"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 364782.0,
      "end_time": 366440.0,
      "text": "avoid predators"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 366730.0,
      "end_time": 368187.0,
      "text": "and approach peahens."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 369800.0,
      "end_time": 372460.0,
      "text": "Why should such an extravagant appendage evolve?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 373767.0,
      "end_time": 375362.0,
      "text": "Even Charles Darwin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 376228.0,
      "end_time": 379627.0,
      "text": "in an 1860 letter to Asa Gray wrote"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 379651.0,
      "end_time": 383423.0,
      "text": "that the sight of the peacock&#39;s tail made him physically ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 383964.0,
      "end_time": 386862.0,
      "text": "He couldn&#39;t explain it with his theory of natural selection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 386886.0,
      "end_time": 388785.0,
      "text": "and out of this frustration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 388809.0,
      "end_time": 391993.0,
      "text": "he developed the theory of sexual selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 393321.0,
      "end_time": 394471.0,
      "text": "On this account,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 394495.0,
      "end_time": 398878.0,
      "text": "the display of the peacock&#39;s tail is about sexual enticement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 398902.0,
      "end_time": 405123.0,
      "text": "and this enticement means it&#39;s more likely the peacock will mate"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 405148.0,
      "end_time": 406482.0,
      "text": "and have offspring."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 407638.0,
      "end_time": 410626.0,
      "text": "Now, the modern twist on this display argument"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 411292.0,
      "end_time": 416262.0,
      "text": "is that the peacock is also advertising its health to the peahen."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 417821.0,
      "end_time": 422948.0,
      "text": "Only especially fit organisms can afford to divert resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 422972.0,
      "end_time": 425669.0,
      "text": "to maintaining such an extravagant appendage."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 426412.0,
      "end_time": 431304.0,
      "text": "Only especially fit men can afford the price that testosterone levies"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 431329.0,
      "end_time": 432598.0,
      "text": "on their immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 433380.0,
      "end_time": 436380.0,
      "text": "And by analogy, think of the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 436620.0,
      "end_time": 443270.0,
      "text": "that only very rich men can afford to pay more than $10,000 for a watch"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 443510.0,
      "end_time": 445301.0,
      "text": "as a display of their financial fitness."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 446933.0,
      "end_time": 449735.0,
      "text": "Now, many people hear these kinds of evolutionary claims"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 449759.0,
      "end_time": 455489.0,
      "text": "and think they mean that we somehow are unconsciously seeking mates"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 455513.0,
      "end_time": 457428.0,
      "text": "who are healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 457452.0,
      "end_time": 460395.0,
      "text": "And I think this idea is probably not right."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 462890.0,
      "end_time": 466951.0,
      "text": "Teenagers and young adults are not exactly known for making decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 466975.0,
      "end_time": 469163.0,
      "text": "that are predicated on health concerns."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 470364.0,
      "end_time": 471965.0,
      "text": "But they don&#39;t have to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 471989.0,
      "end_time": 473472.0,
      "text": "and let me explain why."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 474971.0,
      "end_time": 476322.0,
      "text": "Imagine a population"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 477280.0,
      "end_time": 481206.0,
      "text": "in which people have three different kinds of preferences:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 481230.0,
      "end_time": 484555.0,
      "text": "for green, for orange and for red."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 485742.0,
      "end_time": 486933.0,
      "text": "From their point of view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 486957.0,
      "end_time": 489320.0,
      "text": "these preferences have nothing to do with health;"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 489344.0,
      "end_time": 490836.0,
      "text": "they just like what they like."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 491948.0,
      "end_time": 495989.0,
      "text": "But if it were also the case that these preferences are associated"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 496130.0,
      "end_time": 499100.0,
      "text": "with the different likelihood of producing offspring --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 499350.0,
      "end_time": 501897.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s say in a ratio of 3:2:1 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 502880.0,
      "end_time": 504324.0,
      "text": "then in the first generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 504348.0,
      "end_time": 507620.0,
      "text": "there would be 3 greens to 2 oranges to 1 red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 507644.0,
      "end_time": 509830.0,
      "text": "and in each subsequent generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 509854.0,
      "end_time": 512559.0,
      "text": "the proportion of greens increase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 513885.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515596.99999999994,
      "text": "so that in 10 generations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 515621.0,
      "end_time": 519395.0,
      "text": "98 percent of this population has a green preference."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 519783.0,
      "end_time": 522904.0,
      "text": "Now, a scientist coming in and sampling this population"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 522928.0,
      "end_time": 526577.0,
      "text": "discovers that green preferences are universal."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 527426.0,
      "end_time": 531298.0,
      "text": "So the point about this little abstract example"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 531322.0,
      "end_time": 535982.0,
      "text": "is that while preferences for specific physical features"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 536600.0,
      "end_time": 538569.0,
      "text": "can be arbitrary for the individual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 539910.0,
      "end_time": 541680.0,
      "text": "if those features are heritable"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 545520.0,
      "end_time": 549211.0,
      "text": "and they are associated with a reproductive advantage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 549235.0,
      "end_time": 550449.0,
      "text": "over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 550473.0,
      "end_time": 552400.0,
      "text": "they become universal for the group."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 554992.0,
      "end_time": 560193.0,
      "text": "So what happens in the brain when we see beautiful people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 562340.0,
      "end_time": 566368.0,
      "text": "Attractive faces activate parts of our visual cortex"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 566392.0,
      "end_time": 568337.0,
      "text": "in the back of the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 568361.0,
      "end_time": 570303.0,
      "text": "an area called the fusiform gyrus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 570327.0,
      "end_time": 573129.0,
      "text": "that is especially tuned to processing faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 573153.0,
      "end_time": 577167.0,
      "text": "and an adjacent area called the lateral occipital complex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 577191.0,
      "end_time": 579947.0,
      "text": "that is especially attuned to processing objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 580520.0,
      "end_time": 581915.0,
      "text": "In addition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 581940.0,
      "end_time": 587180.0,
      "text": "attractive faces activate parts of our reward and pleasure centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 587420.0,
      "end_time": 589307.0,
      "text": "in the front and deep in the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 589999.0,
      "end_time": 593123.0,
      "text": "and these include areas that have complicated names,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 593147.0,
      "end_time": 595110.0,
      "text": "like the ventral striatum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 595350.0,
      "end_time": 596954.0,
      "text": "the orbitofrontal cortex"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 596978.0,
      "end_time": 599572.0,
      "text": "and the ventromedial prefrontal cortex."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 600552.0,
      "end_time": 604536.0,
      "text": "Our visual brain that is tuned to processing faces"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 604560.0,
      "end_time": 607196.0,
      "text": "interacts with our pleasure centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 607221.0,
      "end_time": 609668.0,
      "text": "to underpin the experience of beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 611539.0,
      "end_time": 615631.0,
      "text": "Amazingly, while we all engage with beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 615655.0,
      "end_time": 617252.0,
      "text": "without our knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 617276.0,
      "end_time": 619340.0,
      "text": "beauty also engages us."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 620298.0,
      "end_time": 622797.0,
      "text": "Our brains respond to attractive faces"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 622821.0,
      "end_time": 625175.0,
      "text": "even when we&#39;re not thinking about beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 626457.0,
      "end_time": 630746.0,
      "text": "We conducted an experiment in which people saw a series of faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 630770.0,
      "end_time": 632473.0,
      "text": "and in one condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 632497.0,
      "end_time": 638730.0,
      "text": "they had to decide if a pair of faces were the same or a different person."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 639727.0,
      "end_time": 642220.0,
      "text": "Even in this condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 642244.0,
      "end_time": 648386.0,
      "text": "attractive faces drove neural activity robustly in their visual cortex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 648410.0,
      "end_time": 651923.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that they were thinking about a person&#39;s identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 651947.0,
      "end_time": 653248.0,
      "text": "and not their beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 654947.0,
      "end_time": 659258.0,
      "text": "Another group similarly found automatic responses to beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 659282.0,
      "end_time": 661445.0,
      "text": "within our pleasure centers."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 662371.0,
      "end_time": 665160.0,
      "text": "Taken together, these studies suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 665853.0,
      "end_time": 670363.0,
      "text": "that our brain automatically responds to beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 670388.0,
      "end_time": 672403.0,
      "text": "by linking vision and pleasure."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 673674.0,
      "end_time": 676540.0,
      "text": "These beauty detectors, it seems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 676780.0,
      "end_time": 677915.0,
      "text": "ping every time we see beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 677940.0,
      "end_time": 680634.0,
      "text": "regardless of whatever else we might be thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 682842.0,
      "end_time": 688331.0,
      "text": "We also have a \"beauty is good\" stereotype embedded in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 689532.0,
      "end_time": 691759.0,
      "text": "Within the orbitofrontal cortex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 691783.0,
      "end_time": 693558.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s overlapping neural activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 693582.0,
      "end_time": 697366.0,
      "text": "in response to beauty and to goodness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 699500.0,
      "end_time": 702527.0,
      "text": "and this happens even when people aren&#39;t explicitly thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 702551.0,
      "end_time": 704154.0,
      "text": "about beauty or goodness."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 705726.0,
      "end_time": 709685.0,
      "text": "Our brains seem to reflexively associate beauty and good."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 710510.0,
      "end_time": 714488.0,
      "text": "And this reflexive association may be the biologic trigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 714512.0,
      "end_time": 717194.0,
      "text": "for the many social effects of beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 717877.0,
      "end_time": 722271.0,
      "text": "Attractive people receive all kinds of advantages in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 723376.0,
      "end_time": 726130.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re regarded as more intelligent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 726154.0,
      "end_time": 727757.0,
      "text": "more trustworthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 727781.0,
      "end_time": 731325.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re given higher pay and lesser punishments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 731350.0,
      "end_time": 734720.0,
      "text": "even when such judgments are not warranted."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 735392.0,
      "end_time": 738732.0,
      "text": "These kinds of observations reveal beauty&#39;s ugly side."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 739616.0,
      "end_time": 741689.0,
      "text": "In my lab, we recently found"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 741713.0,
      "end_time": 746635.0,
      "text": "that people with minor facial anomalies and disfigurements"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 746659.0,
      "end_time": 750443.0,
      "text": "are regarded as less good, less kind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 750467.0,
      "end_time": 754898.0,
      "text": "less intelligent, less competent and less hardworking."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 755674.0,
      "end_time": 760958.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, we also have a \"disfigured is bad\" stereotype."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 762218.0,
      "end_time": 768876.0,
      "text": "This stereotype is probably exploited and magnified"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 768900.0,
      "end_time": 771313.0,
      "text": "by images in popular media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 771337.0,
      "end_time": 775233.0,
      "text": "in which facial disfigurement is often used as a shorthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 775257.0,
      "end_time": 777915.0,
      "text": "to depict someone of villainous character."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 779198.0,
      "end_time": 782651.0,
      "text": "We need to understand these kinds of implicit biases"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 782676.0,
      "end_time": 784413.0,
      "text": "if we are to overcome them"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 784437.0,
      "end_time": 788118.0,
      "text": "and aim for a society in which we treat people fairly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 788142.0,
      "end_time": 792557.0,
      "text": "based on their behavior and not on the happenstance of their looks."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 796578.0,
      "end_time": 799823.0,
      "text": "Let me leave you with one final thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 800864.0,
      "end_time": 802912.0,
      "text": "Beauty is a work in progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 804347.0,
      "end_time": 807554.0,
      "text": "The so-called universal attributes of beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 807578.0,
      "end_time": 813660.0,
      "text": "were selected for during the almost two million years of the Pleistocene."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 813764.0,
      "end_time": 818656.0,
      "text": "Life was nasty, brutish and a very long time ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 819834.0,
      "end_time": 825157.0,
      "text": "The selection criteria for reproductive success from that time"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 825182.0,
      "end_time": 827470.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t really apply today."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 827786.0,
      "end_time": 829276.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 829300.0,
      "end_time": 833367.0,
      "text": "death by parasite is not one of the top ways that people die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 833391.0,
      "end_time": 836281.0,
      "text": "at least not in the technologically developed world."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 837817.0,
      "end_time": 840177.0,
      "text": "From antibiotics to surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 840201.0,
      "end_time": 843693.0,
      "text": "birth control to in vitro fertilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 843717.0,
      "end_time": 847107.0,
      "text": "the filters for reproductive success are being relaxed."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 847776.0,
      "end_time": 850430.0,
      "text": "And under these relaxed conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 850455.0,
      "end_time": 854689.0,
      "text": "preference and trait combinations are free to drift"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 854713.0,
      "end_time": 856482.0,
      "text": "and become more variable."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 857236.0,
      "end_time": 861422.0,
      "text": "Even as we are profoundly affecting our environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 862805.0,
      "end_time": 866117.0,
      "text": "modern medicine and technological innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 866142.0,
      "end_time": 867895.0,
      "text": "is profoundly affecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 867919.0,
      "end_time": 871641.0,
      "text": "the very essence of what it means to look beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 873170.0,
      "end_time": 875567.0,
      "text": "The universal nature of beauty is changing"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 875591.0,
      "end_time": 878512.0,
      "text": "even as we&#39;re changing the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 880683.0,
      "end_time": 881867.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 881892.0,
      "end_time": 885478.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}